placeDesc: One hour’s walk from the Jablanac port the remains of a German WWII ship can be seen in just a few meters of clear water in Zavratnica bay.
placeShortDesc: The remains of a sunken WWII military ship wreck visible through clear water.
placeRelatedPlaces: The Wreck of the Dorcas Pendell,Gilbert’s Bar House of Refuge,Wreck of the Francisco Morazan,Hulk of the SS Good News
